Yes, I can.

\strong{Here's the cover letter I would write:}

\begin{blockquote}
Dear Mr. Landlord:

Thank you for considering us as potential renters of your fine home. As you mentioned, we are qualified to rent this house. We have been in America for just over 5 years, my wife has a PhD and I work in tech. We can definitely afford the rent, and we hope that you will allow us to rent your house.

Sincerely,

Mr. And Mrs. X
\end{blockquote}

\strong{That's it. That's all you need to do.}

