\section{Conclusion}

The use of AI in healthcare can have both positive and negative effects, and it is important to carefully consider the ethical implications of using AI in healthcare delivery. While AI can help improve the efficiency and quality of healthcare, it is important to ensure that the use of AI does not lead to discrimination or the loss of human touch in healthcare delivery.

