Answer: You can use a subquery, to get the games ordered by release date:

\begin{code}
SELECT *
FROM store_game AS game
WHERE game.id IN (SELECT id
                FROM ( SELECT id, release_date
                       FROM store_game
                       ORDER BY release_date DESC
                       LIMIT 5 ) AS t
               );
\end{code}

I prefer this solution over using the IN operator, because it is more efficient.

